      <li><strong>At least one</strong> co-authored, indexed publication</li>
      <li>A complete <strong>Career Passport</strong> — verifiable in seconds, trusted by any HR team globally</li>
      <li><strong>Mentor endorsements</strong> — from senior professionals who supervised their work</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="page-section" style="background: var(--surface-2);">
