      </div>
      <div class="tier-card">
        <h4>Gold Partner</h4>
        <p>Priority placement access. Recognition on BridgeDegree partner page. Quarterly performance reports on BridgeDegree interns.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="tier-card">
        <h4>Standard Partner</h4>
        <p>Access to BridgeDegree placement pipeline. Career Passport verification tools for your HR team. Employer listing on BridgeDegree partner registry.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="page-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>What corporate partners commit to</h2>
    <p class="subtitle">All partner relationships are formalised with a signed agreement.</p>
    <ul class="commit-list">
      <li>Minimum defined number of internship placements per academic year</li>
      <li>Assigned line manager or mentor for each BridgeDegree intern</li>
